        "headline": "USN-8092-1: Sudo vulnerability",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "It was discovered that Sudo incorrectly checked return codes when dropping privileges to run the mailer. A local attacker could possibly use this issue to escalate privileges.",
          "lang": "en"
        },
