        "headline": "USN-8091-1: util-linux vulnerability",
        "content": {
          "excerpt_text": "It was discovered that the util-linux su utility did not drop capabilities when being used with the --pty option. While not a security issue by itself, a local attacker could possibly use the su tool to exploit vulnerabilities in other applications.",
